{
  "stem": "1765.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I knew a lot, although I had hardly any schooling between '46, March '46, and May, '47.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When Sputnik went up, that was the space program-- in 1956, that was, I wasn't-- '57. '57.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In the fall of '57, Sputnik went up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, and I said to my American friends-- by then I was-- '57, I was in this country already 10 years.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I said, I'm not surprised.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know why you're all surprised.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In Siberia in a small village in the middle of nowhere, we had a rigorous education without paper, without notebooks, without many texts.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We had to share texts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We'd pass them around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But oh, my, we were expected to really work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I loved school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just loved school, even if I failed algebra.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a place to be with, with, with your peers and, and not worry whether the potatoes are rotting It was, it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I loved school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still like going for courses and working with children in schools now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I say my-- I know they say, your face lights up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, yeah, I really love school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It just sort of-- I'm sometimes surprised, I guess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, after we lived with the Segals, as we spoke earlier, in the Russian family, we were then shunted from one place to another, because the Russian couple had a baby.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And maybe they had pulled-- they wanted to get rid of all these eight extra people in this one room.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were split up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My family-- in other words my mother, father, grandmother, and I-- were put with two women and a little boy in a room.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after that, we got our own hut for about eight months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was drafted.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
